subsection.def:
by-election
                    (補選) has the meaning assigned to it by
                    section 2 of the District Councils Ordinance (Cap. 547);

candidate
                    (候選人) has the meaning assigned to it by
                    section 2 of the District Councils Ordinance (Cap. 547);

election
                    (選舉) means an ordinary election or a
                by-election;
